Utilize Endpoint Encryption SolutionsWhy: Ensures data protection through encryption at the endpoint level.Windows:Enable BitLocker with Advanced Encryption Settings:manage-bde -on C: -usedspaceonly -em aes256 -rpUbuntu:Encrypt Home Directory:sudo apt install ecryptfs-utils
sudo ecryptfs-migrate-home -u usernameEncrypt Swap Partition:sudo apt install cryptsetup
sudo cryptsetup luksFormat /dev/sdX
sudo cryptsetup luksOpen /dev/sdX swap
sudo mkswap /dev/mapper/swap
sudo swapon /dev/mapper/swap
